Creates a new {DataStore} using the given configuration, and prepares it
for use.  This method calls  DataStore#prepare , returning the
(promised) DataStore once it's ready for use.  The signature for  {recordMetric}  (if provided) should conform to
 the following:  async function recordMetric(method, id, fields) {
  // {method} is one of "added" | "updated" | "deleted"
  // {id} is the item.id
  // {fields} either:
  // * array strings denoting which fields were changed (if method === "updated")
  // * undefined (otherwise)
}
